{"items":[{"term":"相借問","pronunciation":"sio-tsioh-mn̄g","definition":"動詞。打招呼、寒喧；互相打招呼問候。","fieldNote":"小時候跟阿嬤去菜市場，從巷口走到攤前不到一百公尺，她要相借問三、四次。賣魚的、賣菜的、隔壁的隔壁的鄰居，每個都停下來「食飽未？」「欲買啥？」。我覺得煩，拉她的手叫她快走。她說「人佮人，就是按呢才袂生分」。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/5262/","imageAlt":"相借問","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-480.webp 480w, assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-768.webp 768w, assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"白鑠鑠","pronunciation":"pe̍h-siak-siak","definition":"形容詞（疊字）。形容白得發亮、刺眼的白。","fieldNote":"開學第一天，新買的制服掛在椅背上，白鑠鑠的，連衣領都還沒被汗濕過。媽媽前一晚燙過，皺褶還挺著。早上穿上身，硬得像紙板。走進校門才發現，學長學姐的襯衫都已經奶白色了，只有我們這群新生，遠遠看過去是一排刺眼的白。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/tshiau/?lui=tai_su&tsha=白鑠鑠","imageAlt":"白鑠鑠","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-480.webp 480w, assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-768.webp 768w, assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"四序","pronunciation":"sù-sī","definition":"形容詞。井井有條、妥當；讓人覺得舒服安適的感覺。","fieldNote":"過年前的下午，阿嬤把所有的棉被翻出來曬。傍晚收進來，一床一床拍平、摺好、疊回櫃子。最後一床壓進去，她後退一步看了看，嘴角微微動一下，說「按呢就四序矣」。整個下午的灰塵和陽光味，都關進了櫃子裡。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/1473/","imageAlt":"四序","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-480.webp 480w, assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-768.webp 768w, assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"日頭赤焱焱，隨人顧性命","pronunciation":"Ji̍t-thâu tshiah-iānn-iānn, suî-lâng kòo sènn-miā","definition":"俗諺。大太陽底下，人各自顧自己的命，無力顧及他人。形容人在患難或困境中，以自我保護為主要考量。","fieldNote":"暑假的中午，外面沒有人。連狗都不見了。柏油路面的熱氣一陣一陣往上竄，公車站牌在那裡站著，沒有人等。大人說「日頭赤焱焱」，說這個時候出去是在找死。我趴在窗台往外看，整條街靜著，只有一輛機車遠遠駛過，司機縮著頭。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/26953/","imageAlt":"日頭赤焱焱，隨人顧性命","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-480.webp 480w, assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-768.webp 768w, assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"軟晡","pronunciation":"nńg-poo","definition":"傍晚陽光轉弱的時候。","fieldNote":"家門前的小巷，下午三四點曬得人不敢出去。等到光開始斜、影子拉長，阿公才把椅子搬出來坐。鄰居的貓也在這時候出現，趴在騎樓矮牆上。那個時候叫軟晡——日頭氣勢已經走了，天還沒暗。整條巷子都鬆了一口氣。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/7959/","imageAlt":"軟晡","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/227becfa7ccaad13-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/227becfa7ccaad13-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/227becfa7ccaad13-480.webp 480w, assets/images/227becfa7ccaad13-768.webp 768w, assets/images/227becfa7ccaad13-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/227becfa7ccaad13-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"薄縭絲","pronunciation":"po̍h-li-si","definition":"形容東西厚度很薄或是分量很少。","fieldNote":"清晨出門，阿嬤在廚房聽到開門聲，探頭看了我一眼。我穿著一件薄汗衫。她說「穿甲薄縭絲」，聲音不大，比較像說給自己聽的。我說「沒關係啦」就走了。到了巷口，風吹過來，真的有點涼。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/12340/","imageAlt":"薄縭絲","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-480.webp 480w, assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-768.webp 768w, assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"凊彩","pronunciation":"tshìn-tshái","definition":"副詞，隨便、馬馬虎虎；形容詞，任何；形容詞，隨和、不謹慎。","fieldNote":"外婆炒菜從不量，鹽巴抓一把，醬油沿鍋邊淋一圈，蒜頭用刀背拍扁直接丟進去。我問她放多少，她頭也不抬，說「凊彩仔啦，有啥放啥」，鍋鏟繼續鏟。我站在灶邊，油蒜的味道一陣一陣竄過來，什麼比例都記不起來。但那個菜，我現在還記得味道。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/5755/","imageAlt":"凊彩","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-480.webp 480w, assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-768.webp 768w, assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"日花","pronunciation":"ji̍t-hue","definition":"陽光穿過雲間或葉縫,在地面、水面、牆上形成碎花般閃爍的光影。","fieldNote":"阿公的藤椅上,一塊一塊的光在動。是樹葉在風裡晃,光就跟著晃。小時候我以為那是螢火蟲在白天出來偷跑。後來知道,這個叫日花。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/1171/","imageAlt":"日花","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-480.webp 480w, assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-768.webp 768w, assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}}]}
